Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你看著我的眼睛說\NI wanted to look in your eyes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不信任你\NI don't trust you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經準備好成為殉道者了\NI'm prepared to die a martyr.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼樣才能贏得你的信任\NWhat can I do to earn your trust?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快讓開\NStep away, now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別打了\NCome on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我\NThe fuck off me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了 結束了\NHe's dead, it's over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 冷靜\NEasy. Easy. Take it easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本區域安全\NArea's secure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想殺了他們 過去把他們都殺了\NYou wanted to kill them all, and then go on killing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是挺極端的\NPretty extreme, don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得一點也不極端\NNo, I don't think that's extreme at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們這樣的人\NI think people like that deserve to die{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得讓他們死的很難看\Nin the worst ways you can imagine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於你父母的死 你還記得多少\NWhat do you remember about your parents' death?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一場車禍\NCar crash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時在馬薩諸塞州\NI was in Massachusetts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在突尼斯\NThey were in Tunisia at the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時14歲\NI was 14.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只記得這些\NThat's what I remember.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的行為舉止方面有些問題\NYou started having discipline problems.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾被三個寄宿學校退學\NGot yourself kicked out of three boarding schools.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 只是不知道為什麼會這樣\NYeah, yeah. I know. I wonder what that was about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談談那個沙灘上發生的事\NLet's talk about what happened after that day on the beach.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天 又談這個 你在逗我麼?\NOh, Jesus Christ. Again? Are you kidding me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 又談這個\NYeah, again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那之後是不是就自暴自棄了\NYou gave up everything after that, didn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本科在布朗大學就讀\NYour grad studies at Brown University.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了興趣\NI must have lost interest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對一切都失去了興趣?\NIn everything?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這樣\NNo, not everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見 費雷恩博士\NSee you later, Dr. Frain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天 同一時間見面麼\NSee you tomorrow, same time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換個新面孔來見你\NI like the new look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾琳·肯尼迪\NIrene Kennedy, CIA Deputy Director{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中情局反恐部副主任\Nin charge of Counterterrorism.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是誰\NI know who you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你在這呆了多久麼\NAny idea how long you been here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30天\N30 days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠你想通一些事了\NEnough time for you to figure out a couple things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 關於我自己的事 我想通了不少\NYeah, yeah. I've figured out a lot about myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過的很充實 謝謝\NIt's been a very reflective time. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時在現場你可能撐不過20秒\NYou wouldn't have made it through the next 20 seconds there alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天知道呢\NI guess we'll never know now, will we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴費雷恩博士 說你要殺掉曼蘇爾\NYou told Dr. Frain you thought you were gonna kill Mansur{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掃平他的老巢\Nand wipe out his whole cell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是個開始\NFor starters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 你心裏還打著更大的算盤吧\NYou had an even bigger agenda, didn't you, Mitch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼想的\NWhat did you think,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想一個又一個掃平恐怖分子的據點?\Nyou were gonna jump from cell to cell taking out terrorists?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏟奸除惡?\NRighting the world's wrongs?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這不是搞定了曼蘇爾麼\NGot to Mansur, didn't I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你有能耐啊\NI mean, it's more than you accomplished.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你說一些事\NI'm gonna let you in on something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這的人不知道要拿你怎麼辦\NOur people here, they don't know what to do with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人就覺得把你扔進一個高級別監獄就行了\NA lot of them think we should just throw you in a supermax.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於我嘛\NMe?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 我對你的計劃很感興趣\NI like your agenda, Mitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你加入我們 我可以幫你實現你的目標\NI can help you with it, if you throw in with us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們甚至可以把你培養成專業的特工\NWe can teach you how to play with the big boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我先打斷你一下\NYeah, let me stop you right there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您認為我18個月前沒考慮過\NYou don't think I considered that 18 months ago?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入中情局麼\NJoining the CIA?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己一個人行動幹掉曼蘇爾\NI made the decision to pursue Mansur on my own{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我覺得我自己能辦到\N'cause I knew I could get it done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要明白 只有我才能幫你\NWhat you need to understand is that I'm the only way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達成你的目的\NTo get what you want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要相信你\NWhy the hell would I trust you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我相信你\NBecause I believe in you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只能指望我了\NAnd I'm all you've got.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已確認\NWhat's been confirmed is{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個退役的俄國\Nthe enriched plutonium has been stolen{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核設施裏的濃縮鈾遭竊\Nfrom a decommissioned Russian nuclear facility.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們找到一個核起爆器\NIf they get their hands on a nuclear trigger{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再找一個能造核彈的物理學家\Nand a physicist to build it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就能裝備核武器 引爆核彈\Nthey'd be able to arm it and detonate it at any time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆?\NTom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的測試結果十分優秀\NHe's testing through the roof.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過這麼厲害的\NMight be the best I've ever seen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們監控了他6個月\NWe've had him under surveillance for six months.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關注了他的格鬥術 槍法\NMartial arts, gun skills.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前監控過不少這種民間人員\NI've surveilled dozens of these vigilantes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很與眾不同\NThis one is different.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 這些情況我都清楚\NYeah, well, I've gone over these, Irene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不服從命令 難以控制\NHe's noncompliant, he's oppositional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟著他找到了曼蘇爾的老巢\NHe got us into Mansur's cell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我們強太多了\NThat's a hell of a lot more than we ever managed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶星是我們這的\NAll right, Orion is an elite unit, Irene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密精英特種部隊\NA secret unit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只向你我二人報告\NReports to you, me, and no one else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想為這人\NI don't want to be responsible{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能鬧出的亂子負責\Nfor that kind of mistake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說話的語氣和赫爾利一樣啊\NNow, that's Hurley talking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他給我打了兩次電話 就談這個\NYeah, well, he's called me twice about this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的人能把他嚇壞\NThis kind of psych profile scares the hell out of him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他估計會覺得\NAs far as he's concerned,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給他派了個一心想復仇的瘋子\Nyou're sending him a Section 8 with an ax to grind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沙灘上發生的事\NWhat happened to that kid on the beach,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變了他的一生\Nit changed him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算通過訓練 你也不可能對任何人起那麼大的影響\NYou can't train that into someone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在的心理狀況正是我夢寐以求的\NHis psych profile is exactly what I've been looking for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做過測謊儀測試麼\NPolygraph?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完美通過\NFlying colors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就祝赫爾利好運吧\NAll right. Good luck with Hurley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳\NOh, Irene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個小時內會收到\NWe'll have fresh intel on the Russian{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於俄羅斯濃縮鈾事件的情報\Nplutonium situation in two hours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持電話聯繫\NStay by your phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把眼罩摘下來了\NYou can take the blindfold off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 關於這傢伙 有什麼我要知道的?\NSo, what do I need to know about this guy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是說斯坦·赫爾利麼\NStan Hurley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個勇士\NHe's a warrior.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前海豹突擊隊特種兵\NEx-Navy SEAL.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親和他一起在波斯灣服役過\NMy daddy served with him in the Persian Gulf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你負責這個項目麼\NDid you go through this program?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是瞭解情況 不負責這個計劃\NI went through a program. Not this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個計劃不只是培養一個間諜\NIt's not like becoming a spy or Special Ops,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者特工那麼簡單\Nnone of those things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\NGood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 你的目標是什麼\NSo, what are your goals, Mitch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標?\NMy goals?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標就是如果他們知道我要來了\NMy goal is to have them lie awake at night,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嚇得睡不著覺\Nknowing I'm coming for them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不抽煙了?\NI thought you were supposed to be on the patch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:22:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看了他的測試結果麼\NYou saw those tests.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:22:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看了\NYeah, I saw them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:22:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分優秀\NHe's off the charts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優秀的人我也見過\NI've seen off the charts before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊出身的人員可能會養成一些難以擺脫陋習\NAnd he's got none of the bad habits{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而他就不必了\Nhe'd have to unlearn if he had military training.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難以擺脫?\NUnlearn?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦\NCome on, Stan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你手下的那些海豹突擊隊進大城市裏試試\NYou drop one of your Navy SEALs in an urban setting,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.77,0:23:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的人能輕鬆發現他們是當兵的\Nyou can spot the boot camp on them a mile away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 現在不是..\NWe're not fighting the...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是冷戰那時候了 我知道\NCold War? Yeah, I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副主任女士 你一直在提醒我這點\NYou keep telling me that, Miss Deputy Director.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天 你這麼尊敬我了\NOh, wow. "Miss Deputy Director."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父親會支持我這麼做的\NYour daddy would agree with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每48小時聯繫你一次\NI'll be checking in with you every 48 hours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早上坐飛機去倫敦\NI'm on a plane to London in the morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去抽幾根吧\NAnd go back on the patch, for God's sake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我失望\NDon't prove me wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不會回來了\NShe ain't coming back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\NHey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著我\NEyes front and center.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NSorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉? 你以為我是你的大學教授麼\N"Sorry"? Do I look like one of your college professors?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子 你要稱呼我為"長官"\NYou talk to me, you call me "sir," son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官\NYes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.23,0:24:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽的來這幹什麼呢\NWhat the fuck you doing here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是\NDid you have some bad things happen to you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.13,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些不幸的事發生在你身上\Nsome shitty things happen to you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想把那些恐怖分子趕盡殺絕\NNow you wanna kill those mean old terrorists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些你口中所謂的「壞人」\NGo get some bad guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.97,0:24:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什麼認為\NWhat makes you think you can make it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.10,0:24:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能通過我的選拔?\Nthrough my selection process?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.34,0:24:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我能說話麼 長官\NPermission to speak, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.04,0:24:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 說吧 有話直說\NSure, go ahead if you got something to say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.91,0:24:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你來這 就是個錯誤\NLike this is all a big mistake and you wanna go home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.84,0:24:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想回家麼\NYou wanna go home? Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.31,0:24:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊滾吧 要不然我幫你滾\NGet the fuck out of here. I'll drive you myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.35,0:24:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想 長官\NNot at all, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們還是直入主題吧\NI was gonna suggest we maybe speed this whole thing up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.85,0:24:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆過幾招\NMy guess is, if you and I go hand-to-hand,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.35,0:24:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能否通過\Nyou could probably figure out inside of 20 seconds{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.15,0:24:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的選拔\Nwhether or not I have what it takes to make it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.49,0:24:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看便知\Nthrough your selection process.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.96,0:24:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您覺得呢\NSo, what do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.43,0:24:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你一張床 一個儲物櫃\NWe got an empty cot, empty footlocker.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.53,0:24:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你夠不夠格留在這裏了\NThey're both yours as long as you can last.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.50,0:25:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得可以\NSounds good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.27,0:25:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來\NFollow me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.04,0:25:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會見\NSee you out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.31,0:25:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一句 我聽說了不少關於你的事\NHeard a lot about you, by the way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.58,0:25:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看看你有多大的能耐\NExcited to see what you got.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.26,0:25:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來殺我\NKill me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.93,0:25:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有人以為這樣就能要我的命\NPeople think you can slice a man's throat like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.47,0:25:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有拍電影才可能這麼容易\NThat's only in the movies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這\NRight there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力壓下去\NDo it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.27,0:25:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有動靜 不會搞成亂攤子\NNo noise. No mess.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.18,0:25:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維克多 你來\NVictor, you're up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.23,0:26:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我操\NWhat the fuck, man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.90,0:26:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰他媽帶了把刀\NWho grabs a fucking blade?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.25,0:26:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊\NCome on, you fuckin' pussy. Let's go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該注意到後面的情況\NYou gotta have eyes in the back of your head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.63,0:26:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猶豫一下 就死了\NYou flinch, you die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.57,0:26:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶座計劃的核心就是完成任務\NOrion is about the mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.40,0:26:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能者就上\NIt ain't about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.14,0:26:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是戰死沙場 你就是個孤魂野鬼\NYou go down out there, you're a ghost, you don't exist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.24,0:27:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會回來救你的\NThere's nobody, nobody coming back for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.95,0:27:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你被俘了\NYou're about to be captured.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.39,0:27:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就告別這個世界吧\NBye-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.30,0:27:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在瞭解到\NWe now know 15 kilos of plutonium-239{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.50,0:27:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯那邊有15千克的鈽-239不翼而飛\Nwent missing during the Russian breach.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.37,0:27:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足夠造一個核武器了\NIt's enough to build a full-scale nuclear weapon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.44,0:27:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但可能需要傾全國之力才能完成核武器的建造\NBut that would likely require the resources of a nation-state.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.58,0:27:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為伊朗參謀總長\NAs Iranian Chief of General Staff,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.44,0:27:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們對此事同樣關切\NI share your concern.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.41,0:27:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們同你們一樣 都在關注事態發展\NWe have been monitoring the situation as you have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.38,0:27:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不知道是什麼情況\NI'm afraid we too are in the dark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.42,0:27:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對伊朗來說 建造核武器\NFor Iran, of course,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.45,0:27:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能的\Na nuclear weapon is off the table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.32,0:27:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們簽訂了條約的\NWe have a treaty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些伊朗人對這個條約不太滿意\NYou have countrymen who are not too happy about that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.53,0:27:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們監控了你們的濃縮項目\NWe monitor your nuclear enrichment program pretty closely,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.13,0:28:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現有人在俄羅斯黑市上購買了這些鈽-239\Nbut black market plutonium-239 from Russia...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.97,0:28:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於黑市的情況 高層無從得知\NWould be difficult for inspectors to detect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.57,0:28:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是肯尼迪女士 對吧?\NMs. Kennedy, yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.57,0:28:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為伊朗國防部長 我向您保證\NI assure you as Minister of Defense{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.98,0:28:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道如果我們伊朗\Nthat we in Iran recognize how much the spirit of comity{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.21,0:28:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過任何途徑購買鈽燃料\Nbetween our nations would be compromised{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.68,0:28:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會影響到我們的國家利益\Nif we were to acquire{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有違國際精神\Nweapons-grade plutonium from any source.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.75,0:28:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此\NYes, it would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.36,0:28:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話對伊朗境外的勢力同樣適用\NSame goes for your clients outside Iran,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.03,0:28:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真主黨 哈馬斯\NHezbollah. Hamas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.66,0:28:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡塞武裝\NThe Houthis.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.40,0:28:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論在誰的手中 核武器都是危險的\NNuclear weapons are a danger in any hands, Director.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.23,0:28:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是你們入侵\NWasn't that your pretext for your invasion{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們鄰國的理由麼\Nof our neighbor to the west?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.77,0:28:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50萬伊拉克人喪生\NOne that cost 500,000 Iraqi lives{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.31,0:28:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下一片廢墟\Nand left a wake of destruction{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.67,0:28:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個地區至今動盪不安\Nfrom which our region has never recovered.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.61,0:28:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯塔米將軍 我們是掌握了確鑿的情況才來這會面的\NGeneral Rostami, we came only to tell you what we know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.05,0:28:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這算是威脅我們麼\NIs that a threat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.12,0:28:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是 比赫茲部長\NOf course not, Minister Behruz.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.45,0:29:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位先生 感謝參加這次會面\NGentlemen, I very much appreciate you meeting with us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.19,0:29:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客氣了\NNot at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.66,0:29:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很遺憾 不能給你們提供更多情報\NI only wish we could offer more insight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.13,0:29:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝您的支持\NThank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.60,0:29:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信那個羅斯塔米將軍\NI don't trust General Rostami.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.64,0:29:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要低調行事\NWe need to keep this quiet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.21,0:29:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶座計劃進行的怎麼樣了\NHow ready is Orion?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.81,0:29:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去問問赫爾利\NI'll check in with Hurley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.28,0:29:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼好幾個小時了都沒人來\NWhy is there no one on watch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.15,0:29:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們死定了\NYou're all dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.55,0:29:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊 知道了\NYeah, yeah. I got it, I got it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.69,0:29:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死了\NYou're dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.16,0:29:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼 快說啊\NYou wanna say something to me? Say it. Go on, say it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.67,0:29:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你們30秒收拾\NYou got 30 seconds!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.54,0:30:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是你們的目標\NThese are your targets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.14,0:30:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住他們\NMemorize them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.14,0:30:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要能辨認出他們來\NIt's your responsibility to be able to identify them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.68,0:30:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉一個武裝人員 得一分\NYou shoot a combatant, you get a point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.55,0:30:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒擊中的話 會受到一次電擊\NYou miss, you get a shock.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.59,0:30:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非戰鬥人員 會受到更強的電擊\NYou shoot a noncombatant, you get a bigger shock.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.56,0:30:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果武裝人員擊中了你\NCombatant shoots you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.09,0:30:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就這麼說吧 你那時候會感覺到的\NLet's just say you're gonna feel it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.56,0:30:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎\NReady?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.26,0:30:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始\NGo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.23,0:31:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利在幹什麼\NWhat's Hurley doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.64,0:31:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他腦子出問題了\NHe's fucking with his head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.61,0:31:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操\NFuck!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.81,0:32:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這狗屁的模擬訓練\NFucking AR bullshit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.94,0:32:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧\NShall we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.21,0:32:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NOkay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.37,0:32:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺不錯的\NThat's clever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.81,0:32:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈽原料\NRaw plutonium.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.45,0:32:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前商量好的 是濃縮的\NHighly enriched, as promised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.98,0:32:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此\NLet's hope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.92,0:32:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們 聽到儀器發出響聲真是太棒了\NWow, that's a beautiful sound, gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.79,0:32:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就拿走了\NMay I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.26,0:32:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\NOkay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.90,0:32:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快轉賬\NWire the money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.53,0:32:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就轉\NThat, I can do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.30,0:33:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就拿手機\NThis is a cell phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.20,0:33:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的車開走 有一個重要官員要經過這裏\NGotta move all the vans. The Cardinal's visiting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.29,0:33:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NOkay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.75,0:33:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘內就走\NOkay. Five minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.83,0:33:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車裏的是什麼\NWhat's going on in there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.34,0:33:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀念品\NSouvenirs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.38,0:33:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是緊急情況 請求增援\NPossible code red, backup needed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.80,0:33:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張 沒什麼情況\NThere's nothing going on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.30,0:33:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來看看嘛\NCome in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.40,0:34:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前看來\NIt now appears that all seven victims{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.80,0:34:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7名死者\Nwere shot with a single weapon,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.47,0:34:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死於同一把手槍下\Nbelieved to be a Glock 29.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.44,0:34:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車內發現了武器級鈽的蹤跡\NTraces of weaponized plutonium{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.94,0:34:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時還發現了\Nwere detected inside the van{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.51,0:34:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三具俄羅斯人\Nwhere the bodies of three Russians{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.07,0:34:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和兩具波蘭警察的屍體\Nand two Warsaw police officers were found.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.54,0:34:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯政府已經確認\NThe Russian government has confirmed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.58,0:34:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核燃料的化學指紋表明\Nthat the chemical footprint of the plutonium in question{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.41,0:34:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是托博爾斯克\Nis a match to the plutonium that was stolen{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.42,0:34:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄核設施內\Nfrom the decommissioned{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.68,0:34:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失竊的鈽燃料\Nprocessing facility in Tobolsk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.82,0:34:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蘭警方正在和國際刑警組織合作\NSecurity footage is being analyzed by Polish police,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.82,0:34:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分析監控錄像\Nnow working in conjunction with Interpol,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.99,0:34:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試圖確認槍手的身份\Nto identify the shooter and his connection{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.06,0:34:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查他與鈽燃料失竊案之間有何聯繫\Nto the missing plutonium.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.76,0:34:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍手的身份尚不得知\NThe identity of the shooter remains unknown...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.42,0:35:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 打擾一下\NHi, excuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.86,0:35:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼我能幫你的\N- How can I help you? - Question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.64,0:36:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 需要我幫你麼\NMay I help you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.84,0:36:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 謝謝\NNo, thanks. I'm okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.93,0:36:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N- Ow! Ow! Ow! - Hey! Hey! Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.93,0:36:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普 媽的\NRapp! God damn it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.43,0:36:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要控制住自己\NYou have to stay under control.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.53,0:36:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽的\NDickhead!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.76,0:36:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不知道什麼時候住手\NAsshole doesn't know when to quit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.43,0:36:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在逗我麼 我剛剛救了你\NYou're kidding me, right? I just saved your ass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.43,0:36:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普 你要知道什麼時候該停手\NYou've gotta know when the mission's been accomplished, Rapp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.70,0:36:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 長官 這傢伙.. - 聽著\N- Sir, he's a fucking... - Which he did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.20,0:36:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為你只有眼前這一個目標\NNever assume your target is the only target.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.54,0:36:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人可能看起來沒什麼威脅 但實際上心狠手辣\NThe enemy dresses like a deer and he kills like a lion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.54,0:36:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要像他們一樣心狠手辣\NAnd that's what we gotta do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.68,0:36:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能表現更出色\NWe just gotta do it better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.95,0:36:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣吧\NAll right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.82,0:36:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋\NYou're an asshole.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.93,0:37:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出事了\NWe got a problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.03,0:37:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六周前 有人闖入\NSix weeks ago, there was a breach{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.60,0:37:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯的一個廢棄鈽燃料設施\Nat a decommissioned Russian plutonium facility.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.97,0:37:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了\NI'm aware.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.94,0:37:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不知道 有15千克的鈽燃料失竊了\NWhat you don't know is 15 kilos of plutonium went missing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.58,0:37:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是武器級的\NWeapons-grade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.04,0:37:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多\NThat's a shit-ton of plutonium.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.98,0:37:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼落入他人之手\NAnd it just changed hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.25,0:37:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想給你看點東西\NI wanna show you something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.82,0:37:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個\NTake a look at this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.86,0:37:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該認識這張臉吧\NDoes that face bong a gong for you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.93,0:37:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是只有我一個覺得這人很熟悉\NOr is it just me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.87,0:37:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是他\NIt can't be him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.27,0:37:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在轟炸了巴馬科的大使館之後 我們派出無人機又確認了一次\NOur drones took him out after the embassy bombing at Bamako.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.80,0:37:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法完全確定屍體身份\NWe never got a positive ID.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.71,0:37:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們這的叛逃特工\NThat's our mad dog out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.54,0:38:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那行 我們先假設是他\NAll right. Let's say it's him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.01,0:38:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 不用假設 就是他\NIt's him, Irene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.75,0:38:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有一個一石二鳥的機會\NThis gives us a chance to kill two birds with one stone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.68,0:38:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆迪·沙裏夫\NHamdi Sharif.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.62,0:38:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一個武器販子 目前在土耳其\NHe's an arms dealer working out of Turkey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.16,0:38:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四周前他買了一個俄羅斯設計的核裝置起爆器\NFour days ago, he purchased a Russian-designed nuclear trigger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.02,0:38:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定打算把這玩意轉手\NAnd he's gonna be selling it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.99,0:38:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙裏夫手上有誘餌\NSharif's got the honey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.63,0:38:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只需等待獵物上鉤\NNow we just wait for the bee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.86,0:38:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們派人破壞他們的交易\NWe go in, we fuck up their deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.10,0:38:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他們都幹掉\NAnd we take 'em both out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.64,0:38:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去伊斯坦布爾\NYou're going to Istanbul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.58,0:38:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們那邊有特工接應\NWe have an agent in place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.78,0:38:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會在機場接你\NShe'll meet you at the airport.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\NAll right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.71,0:38:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮卡·奧格登\NAnnika Ogden. We've had her on the ground over there{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.05,0:38:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在那潛伏5年了\Nfor five years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.18,0:38:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓拉普參與這次行動\NI want Rapp on the team.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.79,0:38:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒開玩笑吧\NReally?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.92,0:38:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 他已經準備好了吧\NHe's ready, Stan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.12,0:38:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 我覺得他目前還沒準備好\NActually, Irene, he's not ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.62,0:38:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我會讓他準備好的\NBut he will be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.33,0:39:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長官 找我有事麼\NYou wanted to see me, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.90,0:39:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 把門關上\NYeah. Shut the door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.20,0:39:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有任務了\NWe're shipping out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.57,0:39:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把東西放桌上\NSet those down there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.17,0:39:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡看電影麼\NYou like movies?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.04,0:39:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡\NSure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.15,0:39:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想給你看點東西\NI got something for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.95,0:39:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這他媽是什麼鬼\NWhat the fuck is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.08,0:39:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我也覺得挺操蛋呢\NYeah, I thought so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.82,0:39:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你說什麼\NYou thought so?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.97,0:39:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊\NYeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.15,0:39:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼大難不死呢 拉普\NWhy are you even alive, Rapp?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.02,0:39:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有問過自己這個問題\NYou ever asked yourself that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.33,0:39:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是你 而不是這些人\NWhy you? You know, of all those people?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.10,0:39:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得 肯定是因為你很特別\NYou're special, I guess.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.80,0:39:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NOh, my God!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.97,0:39:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要我調高音量麼\NYou want me to turn it up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.37,0:39:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我願意嫁給你 - 拿著吧\N- I'll marry you! - Take it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.34,0:39:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 把視頻關上\NYou're a fucking coward, you know that? Turn that shit off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.37,0:39:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我媽媽的戒指 你覺得怎麼樣\NWhat do you think? It's my mom's ring.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.37,0:39:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關掉\NYou gonna turn it off?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.01,0:39:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特麗娜!\NKatrina!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:39:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是應該為你感到遺憾\NAm I supposed to feel sorry for you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.92,0:39:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還是不吧\NI don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.13,0:40:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你犯了大錯\NYou made a big mistake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.86,0:40:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓情緒影響到了你的判斷力\NYou let emotion cloud your judgment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.67,0:40:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不要受制於自己的情緒\NNever, ever let it get personal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.37,0:40:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了麼\NYou understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.15,0:40:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\NYeah, I got it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.35,0:40:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好 早上5點出發\NBe ready to go by 5:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.02,0:40:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們4點半見面\NSee you at 4:30.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.13,0:40:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯坦布爾 土耳其\NYou know what you're gonna do here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.67,0:40:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我們來這幹什麼嗎\NNo, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.69,0:40:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不知道 長官 - 嗯\NCorrect. You don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.74,0:40:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多觀察 少說話\NSo keep your eyes open and your mouth shut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.24,0:40:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我命令\NAnd wait for my orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.03,0:41:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆迪·沙裏夫 房地產大亨 武器販子\NHamdi Sharif, a real-estate mogul/arms dealer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.34,0:41:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,養活了不少恐怖分子\NHe's like Santa Claus for terrorists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.27,0:41:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人渣\NScumbag.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.04,0:41:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子 省省你那些\NSpare me your junior-year-abroad{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.94,0:41:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚的看法吧\Nmoral opinion, would you, Rapp?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.71,0:41:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長官 這不只是我的個人看法而已 他就是個人渣\NNot really an opinion, sir. Sharif's a piece of shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.05,0:41:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這不是聖戰\NIt's not a crusade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.45,0:41:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務以實用為重 不要受制於...\NThis mission is practical. Don't make it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.48,0:41:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個人情緒?\NPersonal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\NExactly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.97,0:41:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 長官\NYes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.15,0:41:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維克多 你跟我一起\NVictor, you're with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.95,0:41:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普和安妮卡 你們注意觀察情況\NRapp, you and Annika are eyes on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.96,0:41:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙裏夫日常生活很規律\NSharif has a routine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.33,0:42:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他最近有什麼異常\NLet's see if anything breaks his pattern.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.96,0:42:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白了麼 - 是 長官\N- Got it? - Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.93,0:42:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有48小時完成任務\NAll right, we got 48 hours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.96,0:42:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做的乾淨利索 不留痕跡\NQuick, clean. No footprint.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.33,0:42:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的各股勢力也是錯綜複雜的\NThis town's ready to blow as it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.31,0:42:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\NWhere the hell are you going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.58,0:43:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NExcuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.43,0:43:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這他媽太冒進了\NThat was fucking reckless, Rapp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.17,0:43:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 長官 我這是主動出擊\NI took the initiative, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.87,0:43:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可能會搞砸的 - 但我完成了\N- He could've been made. - Well, I wasn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.54,0:43:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果出來了\NHere we go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.37,0:43:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天上午11點\N11:00 a.m. tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.97,0:43:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同他的情婦見面之前\NA meeting at a restaurant on Akbiyik Street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會去阿克比克街的餐館\NThat's right before Sharif goes to see his mistress.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不符合他平時的日程\NThat breaks his pattern.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.51,0:43:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更關鍵的是\NI'll tell you what'll break his pattern.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.08,0:43:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當他的助理告訴他手機丟了\NWhen that fucking assistant tells his boss{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.55,0:43:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟糕了\Nhe lost his goddamn phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.98,0:43:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不會說的\NHe won't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.25,0:43:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他太怕沙裏夫了 不敢告訴沙裏夫自己搞砸了\NHe's too afraid of Sharif to let him know he screwed up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.05,0:43:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那行 我們明天行動\NAll right. We go tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.06,0:43:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務目標是?\NWhat's the mission, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.36,0:43:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉買家 幹掉賣家\NEliminate the target. Eliminate the recipient.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.16,0:43:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶走貨物\NObtain the package.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.33,0:43:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 貨物是什麼\NAnd what's the package?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.06,0:43:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 到時候就知道了\NWe'll know it when we see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.60,0:43:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打頭陣\NYou're lead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.50,0:43:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做後援\NYou're backup.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.93,0:44:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在街對面監視現場情況\NWe will watch from across the street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.97,0:44:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆扮演一對情侶\NWe get to play lovers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.54,0:44:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆相戀多久了\NHow long have you been married?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.43,0:44:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以為我們已經結婚了\NHe thinks we're married.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.24,0:44:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想太多\NDon't think too much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.31,0:44:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會緊張過頭的\NYou'll lose your nerve.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.64,0:44:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不會\NNo, I don't think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.04,0:44:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你第一次參加任務麼\NIt'll be your first time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.58,0:44:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的腦海中 我已經參加了很多次任務了\NYeah, not in my mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.10,0:45:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老大 目標來了\NLead, your friend's arriving now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.14,0:45:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\NCopy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.55,0:45:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真他媽的是軍隊級別的保護啊\NAnd he brought a shitload of military protection.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.02,0:45:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來搞定他們\NI'll take care of the MPs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.06,0:45:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 別發火嘛\NOh, come on, now, honey. Don't be mad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.70,0:45:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不\NNo, no, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.97,0:45:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有點事 真的\NI had a few. Yeah, I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.44,0:45:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回家後會給你補上的\NI'll make it up to you when I get home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.97,0:45:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的\NYou know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.34,0:46:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝勒貝伊宮附近發現汽車炸彈\NCar bombing, near Beylerbeyi Palace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.38,0:46:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這條消息匯報上去 要不然我就割破你的喉嚨\NCall it in. Call it in, or I'll cut your fucking throat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.48,0:46:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始行動\NLead, you're a go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.35,0:46:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號 進入指定位置\NSurvey 2, get in place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.05,0:46:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小心點 - 我知道的\N- Be careful in there. - I got it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.08,0:46:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NPardon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.76,0:47:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起爆器在轎車裏\NThe nuclear trigger is in the sedan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.53,0:48:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標逃走了\NTarget's gone. Target's gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.43,0:48:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\NGet back!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.20,0:48:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何\NLead?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.80,0:48:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已死亡\NDead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.74,0:48:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務結束\NMission terminated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.27,0:48:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤到安全地點 已確認\NExfil to secure location. Confirm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.31,0:48:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號 快點他媽的確認執行命令\NSurvey 2, you better let me hear you fucking confirm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.71,0:48:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽的 亂成一團了 我們撤\NGod damn it, this is a fucking mess. We're out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.50,0:48:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實點\NDrive! Drive!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.72,0:48:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著你們的老大\NFollow your boss!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.89,0:48:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我 我是他的助手\NPlease, I'm just the assistant!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.35,0:48:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我\NDon't hurt me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.27,0:49:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快開車\NDrive! Drive!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.60,0:49:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住這的五樓\NHe's there right now on the fifth floor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.94,0:49:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做的事我也不喜歡\NPlease I don't approve of what Sharif does.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.16,0:49:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我\NDon't kill me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.35,0:49:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我不會殺你的\NDon't worry, I'm not gonna hurt you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.62,0:49:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標是你的老闆\NI'm gonna hurt your boss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.96,0:49:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起爆器現在在美國人手上\NThe American mercenary has the nuclear trigger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.75,0:49:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞定了我的任務 你搞定你的\NI've done my job. It's your problem now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.73,0:50:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽的\NShit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.81,0:50:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點\NHurry up!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.48,0:50:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快滾開\NCome on, come on, come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.69,0:50:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快滾開\NCome on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.30,0:52:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\NNo, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.53,0:52:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我\NPlease, don't. Don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.57,0:52:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\NNo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.73,0:52:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你違背了我的命令\NYou disobeyed a direct order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.23,0:52:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我決定追蹤目標\NNo, I made a decision to pursue the target,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.86,0:53:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成任務\Nand I completed the mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.50,0:53:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來這就是為了完成任務\NAnd, sir, isn't that what I'm here to do? Isn't that my job?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.44,0:53:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我他媽的要你幹什麼 你就幹什麼\NYour fucking job is to do what I fucking tell you to do!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.41,0:53:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說 你更傾向於讓我離開那\NWhat, you prefer I leave him alive, then,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.85,0:53:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放那人渣一馬咯\Nlet him go? That piece of shit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.29,0:53:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦\NStan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.76,0:53:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你來了 我想給你看點東西\NGood, you're here. I wanna show you something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.00,0:53:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那等著\NWait here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.69,0:53:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這麼下去\NLook at that. That's the kind of bullshit{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.49,0:53:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙會搞砸的\Nthat could shut us down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.80,0:53:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這小子不會遵守命令\NKid can't even follow a fucking order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.01,0:53:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維克托沒辦到的事 拉普辦到了\NVictor got made. Rapp didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.21,0:53:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他媽的 你為什麼這麼看好這個小子\NWhy does this kid give you such a fucking hard-on?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.54,0:53:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別他媽的跟我這麼說話 我是你的上級\NDon't talk to me like that! I'm your superior.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.55,0:53:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的上級? 艾琳\NMy superior, Irene?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.65,0:53:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是你的上級 媽的\NYour superior, God damn it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.72,0:53:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道 我花了多久才找到\NDo you have any idea how long I spent looking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.69,0:53:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼有才 這麼有膽識的小伙子\Nfor someone with that kid's talent and balls?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.22,0:53:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 讓拉普留下\NRapp stays.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.69,0:53:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是命令麼\NYou're giving me an order?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.19,0:53:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\NThat's an affirmative.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.53,0:53:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我跟他單獨談會\NCan you give us a minute?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.56,0:53:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個\NLook at this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.67,0:53:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起爆器肯定在那輛車上\NThe trigger must have been in that car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.64,0:54:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看\NLook at him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.71,0:54:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他\NLookin' at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.11,0:54:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙幹出來的好事\NEverything he did there,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.11,0:54:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我教出來的\NI taught him how to do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.61,0:54:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦\NStan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.25,0:54:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不應該把他從海軍裏招過來\NI should've left him in the Navy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.75,0:54:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要親手殺了他\NI'm gonna kill that son of a bitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.85,0:54:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 斯坦 聽我說\NStan, listen to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.02,0:54:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是\NThe only thing that matters now{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.55,0:54:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個瘋子已經拿到了\Nis that fucking lunatic has everything he needs{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.02,0:54:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制取核武器的全部環節\Nto build a nuclear weapon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.19,0:54:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿到了起爆器 現在要買通一個物理學家\NHe's got a trigger. Now he needs to buy a physicist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.99,0:54:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在要搞清楚\NWe just have to figure out{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.53,0:54:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要在哪造核武器\Nwhere they're gonna build this thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.13,0:54:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本\NBen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.90,0:54:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普從沙裏夫家拿到的那台筆記本電腦\NThat computer our boy Rapp lifted from Sharif's house,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.87,0:54:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯示 有一筆兩百萬美元的款項\Nthere's evidence of a $2 million transfer to a bank account in Rome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.14,0:54:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打到了一家羅馬銀行的賬戶上 等待支取\NCash prepped for withdrawal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.91,0:54:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去羅馬\NRome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.82,0:56:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的錢\NYour money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.15,0:56:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長 我最近讀了一些東西\NI've been reading up, Minister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.72,0:56:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們伊朗人可能從小時候起就知道了\NYou Iranians probably all learn this growing up,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.89,0:56:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簽訂禁核條約前心裏就有數了\Nor at least you did before you signed that treaty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.79,0:56:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到還有這麼些有趣的情況\NBut me, I had no idea about these fun facts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.70,0:56:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你的話我就不會進去\NYeah, I wouldn't do that if I were you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.73,0:56:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起爆點三英里半徑內的人都會蒸發掉\NInside three miles, apparently you just vaporize.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.91,0:56:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些倖免於難\NSome folks don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.11,0:56:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的皮膚會被烤黑 燒焦\NThey get all black and charred,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.11,0:56:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲成一團 沒人知道為什麼會成這個樣子\Nand dense as lead, and no one knows why.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.61,0:56:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五英里半徑內 熱浪席捲一切\NInside five miles, everything is sucked into a void,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.05,0:56:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫度比太陽中心還高\Nhotter than the core of the sun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.19,0:56:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得怎麼樣\NHow about that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.32,0:56:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的錢在哪\NWhere's the rest?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.32,0:56:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了這個再給你們剩下的錢\NYou'll get the rest of your money when the job's done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.30,0:56:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我派來的物理學家呢\NWhere is my physicist?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.20,0:57:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿到錢後 我們把他接過來\NHe'll pick up his money, then we'll pick him up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.01,0:57:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住在羅馬的一家酒店\NHe's staying at a hotel in Rome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.17,0:57:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會在一天內完成武器的組裝\NWe'll need an extra day to configure the weapon, then it's all yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.01,0:57:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們想殺掉多少猶太人就殺多少\NKill as many Jews as you want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.01,0:57:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我們的勝利祈禱吧 兄弟\NDo you practice Salah, brother?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.21,0:57:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到款項 完成任務\NI receive my payment, complete the project.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.89,0:57:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是幹這個的 兄弟\NThat's my practice, brother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.32,0:57:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\NVery well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.72,0:57:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯坦布爾的\NWho was that guy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.32,0:58:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰\NIn Istanbul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.19,0:58:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎總是先我們一步\NIt seemed like he was a step ahead of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.80,0:58:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你打不打算告訴我\NHey, you gonna fill me in here or what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.96,0:58:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些壞人作惡\NThere's some bad people planning on doing some bad things,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.03,0:58:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要阻止他們\Nand it's our job to stop them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.20,0:58:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於維克多 你好像沒說什麼\NYou still haven't said anything about Victor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.10,0:58:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維克多消失了 維克多不存在了\NVictor's gone. Victor doesn't exist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.41,0:58:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普 你覺得我們在這裏是幹什麼的\NWhat is it you think we do here, Rapp?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.15,0:58:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們幹掉那些該死的傢伙\NI think we kill people who need to be killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.09,0:58:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那誰來告訴你應該幹掉誰呢\NAnd who do you trust to tell you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.12,0:58:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 遵守命令就行了\NI follow orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.49,0:58:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想執行命令的時候 才執行命令\NNo, you follow orders when they suit you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.32,0:58:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你加入我們\NThis whole thing is pretty much{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.86,0:58:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是實現自己目標的一種手段\Njust a means to an end for you, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.83,0:58:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長官 我經歷了很多事\NA lot's happened in my life, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.26,0:58:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是麼\NReally? Huh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.26,0:58:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊\NYeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.30,0:58:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你覺得 我們派你到這來\NSo you think you were sent here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.80,0:58:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了給你人生中的遺憾 憤怒\Nas an outlet for your self-pity,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.10,0:58:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愧疚 找個發洩口?\Nand your anger, and all your guilt. Right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.74,0:58:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛國主義之所以還存在\NPatriotism exists{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.77,0:59:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為有你我這樣的人為崇高的事業而奮鬥\Nbecause people like you and people like me need a higher cause.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.84,0:59:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了比我們倆更重要的目標而奮鬥\NSomething bigger than us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.18,0:59:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你腦子裏你認為是"復仇"的玩意\NThat stink coming outta you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.98,0:59:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是狗屁\Nyou like to call "revenge," the rest of us call "shit."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.91,0:59:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沉浸於其中\NAnd as soon as it starts to feel good,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.45,0:59:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不再是一位合格的特工\Nthat's when you stop being a professional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.28,0:59:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的你一文不值\NAnd then what are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.92,0:59:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來說點好消息吧\NTell us something good, darling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.99,0:59:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們入侵了他們的系統\NWe're in their system.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.90,0:59:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一有人把錢從沙裏夫的賬上取走\NThe moment that transfer from Sharif's account is picked up,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.00,0:59:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就能馬上收到消息\Nwe'll know it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.97,0:59:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容像紅海一樣美\NBoy, you just smile, and the Red Sea parts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.31,0:59:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地中海也很美啊\NWorks in the Med, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.27,0:59:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太美艷了\NI'll bet it does.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.32,0:59:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人把沙裏夫賬戶裏的錢取出來了 兩百萬美元\NCash withdrawal from Sharif's account. $2 million, U.S.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.19,1:00:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現那個物理學家了 我們走\NThere's our physicist. Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.24,1:01:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到博斯科洛大酒店 祝您入住愉快\NWelcome to the Boscolo and enjoy your stay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.57,1:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N- Thank you very much. - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.65,1:01:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住1448間\NHe's in 1448.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.02,1:01:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們住他隔壁\NAnd we're next door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.38,1:02:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 密碼\NCode in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.45,1:02:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 維克多-查理 1109.\NVictor-Charlie 1109.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.95,1:02:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已確認\NConfirmed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.55,1:02:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標住1448房 我們住隔壁\NSuite 1448. We're in 1449, right next door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.19,1:02:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那個物理學家 把他帶出來\NAll right. We'll grab the physicist,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.06,1:02:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去接應你們\Nand we'll take out whosever coming for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.26,1:02:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每15分鐘給我打一次信號\NSignal every 15 minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.46,1:03:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\NHey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.07,1:03:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了你的遭遇\NI know what happened to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.24,1:03:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\NI'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.58,1:03:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很能理解你\NI understand you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.32,1:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你認為的更甚\NMore than you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.40,1:03:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道失去我們所愛的人是多麼的心痛\NI know what it's like to lose people you love.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.31,1:03:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要把這些壞蛋繩之以法\NWe're gonna get these fuckers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.35,1:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我靠\NFuck!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.29,1:04:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們他媽的在哪呢\NWhere the hell are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.34,1:04:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利\NHurley... Where is he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.82,1:04:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏\NI don't know what you're talking...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.47,1:05:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在說什麼\NWhere is he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.43,1:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪\NHe outside?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.34,1:05:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外面\NPlease, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.35,1:05:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饒命啊\NPlease.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.35,1:06:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利 什麼鬼\NHurley, what the fuck?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.75,1:06:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在盯梢麼 怎麼沒發現他們\NI thought you were eyes on, why didn't you spot 'em?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.22,1:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們比我們早到賓館\NThey were already in the damn hotel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.52,1:06:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當地的黑手黨在與他們合作\NLocal mafia's working with 'em.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.57,1:06:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會聯繫肯尼迪副主任 已經抓到物理學家了\NI'll tell Kennedy we have the physicist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.17,1:06:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那邊是什麼情況\NWhat the hell just happened out there, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.27,1:06:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙把我們的行動搞砸了兩次\NThat's twice now this guy's blown up our entire op.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.34,1:06:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是什麼\NWhat's the target? Huh? What's the target?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.74,1:06:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道 先生 - 說啊\N- I don't know, mister. - Yeah, you do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.71,1:06:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我看不出來麼\NDo you think I'm stupid?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.18,1:06:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個美國人 他認識你\NHe's an American. He said your name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.52,1:06:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你訓練了他？\NDid you train this guy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.92,1:06:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你喜歡抽煙麼\NYou like to smoke?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.64,1:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的天\NOh, Jesus Christ!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.39,1:06:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你抽煙麼\N- Are you a smoker? - I don't...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.26,1:06:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這習慣可不太妙啊\N- Wait! - Bad habit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.69,1:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 我說我說\NWait, stop! Wait, wait! I know something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.43,1:06:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什麼 - 我說我說\N- What do you know? - I know something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.89,1:06:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們稱那個傢伙為「幽靈」\NThere is a man... There is a man they call Ghost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.60,1:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「幽靈」 那個伊朗人就是這麼稱呼他的\NGhost. I think it was an Iranian man said it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.53,1:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在哪造炸彈\N- Uh-huh. Where are they building the bomb? - I just...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.94,1:06:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他們在哪造炸彈 - 我只是拿了錢而已\N- Where are they building it? - Took the money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.40,1:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在哪造炸彈\NWhere are they building it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.21,1:07:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再給你點時間好好想想\NAll right, here. Take some time to think about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.81,1:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個「幽靈」麼\NGhost. Is that his name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.78,1:07:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他要追蹤你\NWhy is this guy after you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.21,1:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是出於個人原因?\NSomething personal, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.81,1:07:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在造核彈\NThey're building a nuke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.55,1:07:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去納沃納賓館\NHotel Navona.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.62,1:07:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗個澡吧\N- Clean yourself up. - Wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.45,1:07:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別走啊\NDon't go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.56,1:07:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國總統命令美國海軍第六艦隊\NAmerica's president has ordered the Sixth Fleet{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.69,1:07:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開意大利那不勒斯的海軍基地\Nout of the U.S. Naval base in Naples, Italy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.96,1:07:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝西南方向航行\NThe Sixth Fleet is now southwest off the coast...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.83,1:07:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你\NLet me help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.20,1:07:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我自己來\NNo, it's okay. I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.43,1:07:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是我來吧\NYou're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.85,1:07:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天覺得如何\NHow are you holding up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.26,1:08:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天很害怕\NI was afraid today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.79,1:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為我們都要丟命了\NI thought we were going to die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.66,1:08:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要麼一直很害怕 要麼永遠不害怕\NYeah, I'm either always afraid or never afraid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.93,1:08:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我究竟是什麼感受\NI don't know which.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.45,1:08:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貼好了\NThere you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.75,1:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆一會兒吧\NJust relax now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.29,1:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天再去找「幽靈」\NWe'll search for Ghost tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.61,1:08:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你嚇到我了\NYou scared me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.84,1:09:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是誰\NWho are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.78,1:09:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思\NWhat do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.38,1:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前說「幽靈」\NYou said "Ghost."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.38,1:09:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那又怎麼了\NWhat about him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.57,1:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我從來沒提過這個名字\NI never told you that name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.78,1:09:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利告訴過我的\NHurley did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.02,1:09:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就扯淡吧\NYeah, I think you're full of shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.95,1:09:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰\N- Mitch. - Who are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.66,1:09:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有毛病吧 - 你為誰效勞\N- Mitch, what's wrong with you? - Who do you work for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.69,1:09:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是中情局的\NI'm CIA.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.36,1:09:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別他媽的騙我\NNow don't fucking lie to me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.36,1:09:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒撒謊\NI'm not lying!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.93,1:09:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是伊朗人\NYou're Iranian, aren't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.06,1:09:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我\NGet the fuck away from me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.01,1:09:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那幫伊朗人是一夥的?\NAre you working with the Iranians?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.41,1:09:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話\NTell me the truth. Tell me the truth!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.34,1:09:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧\NGo to hell!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.09,1:09:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是伊朗情報部門的麼\NYou Iranian intelligence?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.89,1:09:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是伊朗情報部門的麼\NAre you Iranian intelligence?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.57,1:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於幽靈 你知道多少\NWhat do you know about Ghost?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.56,1:10:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要解密裝置\NWe're gonna need the decryption device.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.36,1:10:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的對 米奇\NYou were right, Mitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.86,1:10:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難讓這個伊朗間諜開口\NThis Iranian mole is a tough nut to crack.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.50,1:10:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只從她那問到了她的接頭人 阿扎德·阿沙尼\NAll I could get from her was her handler. Azad Ashani.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.94,1:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的一個朋友\NHappens to be a friend of mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.07,1:10:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見見他\NI'm gonna go pay him a visit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.47,1:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我跟你一起去\NOkay, I'm going with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.66,1:10:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不行\NNo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.87,1:10:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你待在這\NI need you to stay here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.51,1:10:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪帶了一群中情局\NKennedy's on her way with the CIA team{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.08,1:10:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和摩薩德特工過來\Nand a Mossad team.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.51,1:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定會問我你去哪了\NShe's gonna ask me where you went.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.78,1:10:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼說\NWhat the hell am I supposed to say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.45,1:10:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 自己動點腦子\NThat's right, she is. And you're gonna be smart,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.75,1:10:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說出去\Nand you're gonna keep your mouth shut,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.78,1:10:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掩蓋我的行蹤\Nand you're gonna cover my ass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.51,1:11:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還留著它呢\NI still have it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.41,1:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯啊\NVery nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.71,1:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 見到你 我總是很高興\NI am always happy to meet you, Stan...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.58,1:11:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你每次找我談的事 都讓我高興不起來\NBut never happy why.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.55,1:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我們見面的時候 可以去吃個比薩\NWell, maybe next time we'll meet for pizza.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.12,1:11:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩子挺有骨氣的\NYour girl's tough, by the way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.43,1:11:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對她好點\NGo easy on her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.06,1:11:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的侄女\NShe's my niece.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.80,1:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\NYeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.60,1:11:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼消息要告訴我麼\NWhat have you got for me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.87,1:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事的幕後黑手是羅斯塔米將軍\NThe men behind all this are General Rostami,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.14,1:12:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊朗參謀總長\Nour military chief of staff,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.74,1:12:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有國防部長比赫茲\Nand our defense minister, Behruz.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.65,1:12:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都很有權勢\NBoth are very powerful,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.85,1:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都對禁核協議的簽署心懷不滿\Nand both are very angry about the nuclear treaty we made with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.02,1:12:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去的兩年內他們\NThey have been trying to acquire{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.92,1:12:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直試圖搞到核材料\Nnuclear materials for the past two years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.82,1:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們找來了那個\NAnd they are the ones{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.56,1:12:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫「幽靈」的僱傭兵\Nwho hired the mercenary called Ghost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.83,1:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯塔米在德黑蘭 比赫茲在羅馬\NRostami is now in Tehran, but Behruz is here in Rome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.00,1:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓手下通過他的手機定位到他的位置\NAnnika has been tracking his movements through his cell phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.97,1:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在哪造核彈?\NAnd they're building it here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.14,1:12:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我知道就好了\NI wish I knew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.24,1:12:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們抓住他們的物理學家了\NWe have their physicist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.64,1:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒法做了\NThey can't build it without him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.61,1:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\NBut...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.11,1:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個僱傭兵\NThe mercenary asked Behruz{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.82,1:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫比赫茲找一個伊朗的科學家來\Nto use one of ours, an Iranian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.68,1:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比赫茲同意了 他們匆忙行事\NBehruz agreed. That was rash.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.49,1:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說明他們急於盡快完工\NIt means they are in a hurry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.06,1:12:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目標是以色列?\NAnd the target's Israel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.03,1:13:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想告訴你更多信息\NI wish I had better information for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.27,1:13:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利在哪\NWhere the hell is Hurley?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.87,1:13:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我現在是什麼情況\NYou gotta tell me what's going on here. Now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.74,1:13:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是赫爾利培養出來的麼\NThat guy he trained, who the hell is he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.74,1:13:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你不需要知道這個\NThat's not something you need to know right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.61,1:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在掩蓋什麼\NWhat are you covering up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.68,1:13:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當你有了足夠等級的安全許可\NWhen you've got a level-5 security clearance{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.71,1:13:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了20年的工作經驗 再來找我談這個問題吧\Nand 20 years' experience, talk to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.18,1:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然就閉嘴 乖乖幹活吧\NUntil then, shut up and do your job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.15,1:13:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你們解密並掃瞄她的手機\NI want her cell phone decrypted and scanned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.22,1:13:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當地警方一小時前在港口發現一具屍體\NLocal PD pulled a body from the harbor an hour ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.06,1:13:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部中彈\NGunshot to the chest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.63,1:13:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者是 伊朗情報官員 阿扎德·阿沙尼\NIranian intelligence officer, Azad Ashani.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.76,1:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NChrist!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.03,1:13:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利就是去見他了\NThat's the guy Hurley went to meet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.06,1:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個混蛋\NStupid son of a bitch!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.83,1:13:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們要去找到赫爾利的下落\NAll right, so what do we do? We gotta go after him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.60,1:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在造一個他們的核彈 拉普\NThere's a fucking nuke in play, Rapp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.84,1:13:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到核彈是我們的任務 唯一的任務\NThat's the mission, and the only mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.14,1:13:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎麼看\NThis is now a joint CIA-Mossad operation,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.91,1:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這是中情局和摩薩德的聯合行動\Nwhether we like it or not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.21,1:13:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我撥通局長的電話\NCan you get the Director on the phone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.74,1:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就打算把他棄之於不顧了?\NSo you're just gonna write him off then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.85,1:14:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的計劃?\NThat's the plan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.71,1:14:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦·赫爾利幾乎算得上是我的親人了\NStan Hurley is the closest thing to family I've got.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.92,1:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他現在在場\NAnd if he were standing here right now,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.08,1:14:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只會問一個問題\Nhis only question would be,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.75,1:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要浪費時間去討論他的問題\Nwhy are we wasting our breath talking about him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.06,1:14:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒你的事了\NYou're through here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.29,1:14:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你準備回程 這是命令\NYou're going home, that's an order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.33,1:14:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在給我坐下 閉嘴\NNow, sit down and shut up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.84,1:15:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要幫我\NWhy are you helping me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.94,1:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿沙尼已經死了\NYour handler Ashani was killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.91,1:15:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利去見他了 突遭意外\NHurley was with him. Something happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.78,1:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去追蹤他們\NI'm going after him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.38,1:15:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的幫助\NI need your help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.89,1:15:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得動身了\NWe gotta go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.88,1:15:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦\NStan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.95,1:15:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等這一刻已經很久了\NI've looked forward to this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.01,1:15:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 羅尼\NI'm sure you have, Ronnie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.25,1:15:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要給你看點東西\NI wanna show you something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.02,1:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行啊\NAll right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.90,1:16:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這是不是野蠻人的作為\NSavages. Right, Stan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.83,1:16:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不怪他們\NBut you know something? I don't blame them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.34,1:16:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而怪你\NI blame you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.44,1:16:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不違抗命令\NNever would've happened{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.01,1:16:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會這樣了\Nif you would have followed orders, Ronnie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.21,1:16:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你陣亡了 你就成幽靈了\N"You go down out there, you're a ghost."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.24,1:16:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就消失了\N"You're a John Doe."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.78,1:16:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你被俘了\N"You get captured?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.25,1:16:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我說的話 我真高興\NOh, you remember. That's very gratifying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.41,1:16:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\NThank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.45,1:16:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼 你讓我很自豪\NYou made me proud today, Ron.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.35,1:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該來救我的\NYou should've come for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.99,1:16:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你將更多人置於險境\NTen men would've died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.19,1:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你他媽的沒有遵守命令\NYou put 10 men's lives in danger,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.76,1:16:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你將更多人的生命置於危險之中\N'cause you couldn't follow a fucking order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.79,1:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去你媽的 - 去你媽的命令\N- Fuck you. - Fuck orders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.09,1:16:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是我的性命\N- Fuck the mission! - Fuck you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.83,1:16:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時是你的手下 我信任你\NThis was me. I was your boy, I believe that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.20,1:16:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我對你深信不疑\NYou made me believe that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.91,1:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿沙尼讓手下\NAshani had their people tracking Minister Behruz's{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.88,1:17:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤比赫茲的手機位置\Nsecure cell phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.41,1:17:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到了比赫茲 就找到了赫爾利\NSo, we find Behruz, we find Hurley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.96,1:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇\NMitch!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.43,1:18:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你啊\NOh, yeah, look at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.44,1:18:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是從阿勒頗的那些人那裏學會這招的麼\NDid you learn that in Aleppo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.14,1:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不\NNo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.47,1:18:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 你教過我的 要讓敵人出乎意料\NYou always told us what to expect, Stan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.01,1:18:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在告訴我你的手下在哪\NNow, where's the rest of your team?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.08,1:18:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的天 羅尼\NCome on, Ronnie, really?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.92,1:18:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 別再叫我羅尼了 - 你的手下在哪\NDon't call me that. Where's the rest of your team?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.79,1:18:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手下的那個新人 他一直在找我\NYour new boy out there, he on my tail?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.99,1:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼 這是你犯下的第一個錯誤\NRonnie, Ronnie, Ronnie. There's your first mistake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.46,1:18:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,審訊的時候 不要直入主題\NYou never start with a real question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.46,1:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要循序漸進\NYou start slow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.80,1:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入到受審人的頭腦當中\NYou get inside your subject's head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.30,1:18:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 我再問你一次\NStan, I'm gonna ask you one more time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.23,1:18:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你犯的第二個錯誤\NThere's your second mistake. Number two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.10,1:18:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二個錯誤 就是 不要說「再問你一次」這種話\NYou don't say, "one more time." You already...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.57,1:18:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽的\NDamn!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.91,1:18:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 我犯的第三個錯誤是什麼\NNow, what's that third mistake, Stan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.05,1:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼\NHuh? What is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.01,1:18:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 繼續啊\NGo ahead! Go ahead!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.95,1:19:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有9個指甲呢 真爽\NI got nine more! I like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.45,1:19:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真爽啊 再來啊\NI like it. Go ahead, bring it on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.89,1:19:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你個混蛋\NYou motherfucker!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.92,1:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想知道我們外面是不是有人\NRonnie wants to know if I got a team outside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.33,1:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧\NRight, Ron?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.49,1:19:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能安全的將核彈運走\NIf it's safe to move your bomb.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.46,1:19:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有人在跟蹤我們\NAre we being followed?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.40,1:19:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的這個接班人在哪\NWhere's the new me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.27,1:19:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了調查 我瞭解他的一切情況\NI've done my research. I know all about him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.87,1:19:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說米奇麼\N"The new me..." Oh, you mean Mitch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.37,1:19:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說 米奇是個難以預測的傢伙\NYou know, Mitch, he's unpredictable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.08,1:19:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算不準他的\NYou never know about Mitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.34,1:19:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他行蹤不定\NHe might be here, he might be there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.95,1:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你很像 但你更加瘋狂\NHe's like you, but you're a real Section 8.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.55,1:19:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了\NEnough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.61,1:19:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 操你媽\NSchizo mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.78,1:19:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他們在哪\NWhere are they?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.98,1:19:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你個沒爹養的 - 他們在哪\N- Loser dad. - Where are they?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.62,1:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NGod!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.29,1:19:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手下在哪\NWhere's the rest of your team?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.89,1:19:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去你媽的\NHalf-wit mom, psycho dad...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.36,1:19:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你手下的其他人在哪\NWhere's the rest of your team?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.59,1:19:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這人渣 - 你手下的其他人在哪\N- You're pond scum. - Where are they?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.13,1:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋\NPond scum! You're fucking...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.94,1:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於你接頭人的事 我很難過\NI'm sorry about your handler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.24,1:20:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿沙尼是我的叔叔\NAshani was my uncle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.25,1:20:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是比赫茲和羅斯塔米派人刺殺了他\NI'm sure it was Minister Behruz{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.98,1:20:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們相對以色列發動核戰爭\Nand General Rostami who had him killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.88,1:20:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們試圖組織他們\NThey want nuclear war with Israel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.58,1:20:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在和他們的鬥爭中\NWe tried to stop them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.45,1:20:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的兄弟和父親雙雙喪命\NMy brother and father both died fighting them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.43,1:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這轉彎\NCorviale. Turn here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.66,1:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我最大的錯誤\NYou know what my real mistake was?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.00,1:20:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是信任你\NI trusted you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.34,1:20:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我覺得我能幹出一番大事\NYou made me feel like I was the Second Coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.57,1:20:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就像我的父親一樣\NAnd you acted like my father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.05,1:20:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信賴你 信賴美利堅合眾國海軍\NI trusted you and I trusted the United States Navy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.29,1:21:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國做的事 都是正確的 是麼 斯坦\NU.S. of A. Does it, it's gotta be good. Right, Stan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.33,1:21:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是 從來都沒人告訴我\NExcept{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.66,1:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所負責的究竟是一個怎樣的項目\Nnobody told me the business y'all are really in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.30,1:21:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們製造出怪物\NYou create monsters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.20,1:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是惡果\NThat's just what you do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.70,1:21:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼虐待我的人\NThose people who did this to me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.31,1:21:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他們是野蠻人麼\Nyou think they're barbarians?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.18,1:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扯淡\NBullshit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.18,1:21:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前說的破解做的怎麼樣了\NWhere's the decryption I asked for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.32,1:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開工前拉普把手機拿走了\NRapp grabbed her smartphone before we could get any of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.06,1:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前找不到他\NAnd we can't find him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.22,1:21:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,監控攝像頭顯示\NSurveillance cameras picked up Rapp{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.06,1:21:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他5分鐘前打暈了我們的一個特工\Ntaking out our agents five minutes ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.33,1:21:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在幹什麼呢\NWhat the hell are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.44,1:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏發生的一切\NThere's not a single thing happening here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.41,1:21:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是你一手造成的\Nthat you didn't make happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.61,1:22:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑這操蛋的美國 對吧\NGod bless fucking America, huh, Stan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.25,1:22:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能告訴你米奇在哪\NI can tell you where Mitch is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.15,1:22:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 我犯的第三個錯誤是什麼\NWhat's that third mistake, Stan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.72,1:22:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 米奇.. - 我聽不見你說的話\NMitch... I can't hear you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.16,1:22:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我操\NFuck!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.63,1:22:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你犯的第三個錯誤 永遠不要和敵人站的太近\NThird mistake, never get too close.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.37,1:22:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快搞定你的私事\NFinish your personal business here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.34,1:22:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務已經結束了\NYour work is done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.04,1:22:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈已經裝備好了\NThe bomb is armed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.47,1:22:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 啟動計時器了麼 - 是的\N- Timer is set up? - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.77,1:22:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在耍你\NHe's playing you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.21,1:22:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈是給他造的 不是給你的\NBomb's not for you, it's for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.44,1:22:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是他的計劃罷了\NIt was his plan all along!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.41,1:23:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連不上網絡\NDead zone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.48,1:23:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏收不到任何信號\NWe're not getting any signals here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.36,1:23:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\NWait a second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.48,1:23:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想拿核彈幹什麼\NWhat are you gonna do with it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.31,1:23:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 不是我要幹什麼\NNo, Stan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.18,1:23:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我們要幹什麼\N"What are we gonna do with it?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.62,1:24:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼 為什麼選擇羅馬這個地方啊\NWhy are we in Rome, Ronnie?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.46,1:24:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡羅馬\NI like Rome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.39,1:24:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏食物很好吃\NIt's good food.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.36,1:24:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不要以為 我會戰死沙場\NNever, ever thought I'd die in the field.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.87,1:24:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是覺得我很瘋狂\NAin't it crazy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.10,1:24:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我以後想\NI always figured it would be, I don't know,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.14,1:24:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在一個森林小屋裏 帶著我的狗\Nsome cabin in the woods with my dog.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.51,1:24:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的話嘛\NMe?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.24,1:24:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇過水上生活\NI think I want water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.51,1:24:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死在海裏大概是十分平和的\NThere's just something peaceful about dying at sea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.49,1:24:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\NAll right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.16,1:24:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束這一切吧\NLet's get it over with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.49,1:24:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你想痛痛快快的死\NNo, you'd like that, wouldn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.63,1:24:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會殺了你的\NI ain't gonna kill you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.73,1:24:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦 我要讓你親眼見證\NYou're gonna live to see{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.13,1:24:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一手造成的災難\Nthe crown of your creation, Stan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.50,1:24:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數千美國人將會燒死\NThousands of Americans are gonna burn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.17,1:24:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你\NAll because of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.61,1:25:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好觀賞吧\NEnjoy the show.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.91,1:25:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好準備\NGet ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.55,1:25:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動倒計時\NGo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.28,1:26:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你救救我\NPlease help me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.85,1:27:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮卡\NAnnika.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.05,1:27:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母是好人\NYour family were very well respected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.93,1:27:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是他們的朋友\NThey were my friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.60,1:27:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\NBastard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.27,1:27:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他們很熟\NI knew them very well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.53,1:27:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\NPlease I beg you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.53,1:28:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探測到一起爆炸\NWe've got an explosion detected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.73,1:28:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這\NHere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.37,1:28:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離菲烏米奇諾運河500米處\NA half click off the Fiumicino waterways.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.50,1:28:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸點位於地下\NIt's underground.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.87,1:28:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 德爾塔一號小隊 開始行動 - 出發\N- Delta One, go! - Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.71,1:28:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們坐直升機過去\NGet a chopper out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.00,1:29:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普 你不應該來這的\NYou're not supposed to be here, Rapp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.77,1:29:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎樣 把我開除?\NYeah, what are you gonna do, fire me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.74,1:29:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊還有一條通道 他搞到核彈了\NThere's another passage down there. He's got the nuke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.38,1:29:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你一個人可以吧 - 快去吧\NYou gonna be good?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.44,1:29:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海軍 救援直升機\NGo. Go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.05,1:30:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把槍放下\NPut the gun down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.91,1:30:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然她就死了\NOr she's dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.68,1:30:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 我要去見我的親人\NI want to see my family, Mitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.72,1:30:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 安妮卡\NNo, Annika, you don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.66,1:30:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見我的親人\NI want to see my family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.09,1:30:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 聽話\NCome on, Mitch. Be nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.19,1:30:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想活命\NShe wants to live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.86,1:30:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想去見自己的家人\NShe wants to see her family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.80,1:30:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下槍\NPut the gun down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.73,1:30:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮卡\NAnnika!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.11,1:32:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核彈會爆炸的\NThe bomb can't be stopped.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.87,1:32:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼也做不了 就像那個在沙灘上死掉的女人一樣\NJust like you couldn't stop{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.58,1:32:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你救不了她\Nthat beautiful girl from dying on the beach.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.78,1:32:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳\NIrene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.15,1:32:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核彈在那艘船上\NThe bomb's on a boat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.85,1:32:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利\NHurley?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.19,1:32:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的\NHow do you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.79,1:32:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼向在海上引爆核彈\NRonnie wanted to die at sea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.19,1:32:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是第六艦隊在附近巡邏\NIs the Sixth Fleet out on maneuvers?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.87,1:32:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NOh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.93,1:32:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把偵察衛星都調過來\NBring up ISR feeds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.27,1:32:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派飛機去現場偵查情況\NGet me eyes in the sky over the coastline{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.84,1:33:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知第六艦隊 發出核爆警告\Nand put the Sixth Fleet on nuclear alert.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.81,1:33:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆\NTom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.87,1:33:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是第六艦隊 他們目前離海岸線25英里\NThe target is the Sixth Fleet and it's 25 miles offshore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.78,1:33:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太恥辱了\NIt's a shame.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.35,1:33:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女朋友生前最後看到的一幕是 你沒法救她\NThe last thing your girl saw was you not saving her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.70,1:33:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥警報\NGeneral quarters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.90,1:33:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員回到各自崗位\NAll hands, man your stations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.83,1:33:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是演習 重複一遍 這不是演習\NThis is not a drill. I repeat, this is not a drill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.84,1:33:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一艘攜帶了核裝置的小艇 正在接近中\NInbound, small vessel-borne nuclear device.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.71,1:33:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man decon stations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.11,1:33:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子 赫爾利是沒好好教過你麼\NDidn't Hurley teach you anything, little brother?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.35,1:33:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不要受制於自己的情緒\NTo never make it personal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.06,1:34:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有受制於自己的情緒\NThis isn't personal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.27,1:34:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\NShit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.94,1:34:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核彈上裝了計時器和起爆裝置\NThe bomb has a timer and a release trigger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.25,1:34:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸毀小船會直接引爆核彈\NWe take out his boat, it'll detonate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.88,1:34:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果核彈在水面爆炸\NIf it goes off above the waterline...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.88,1:34:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那會是一場災難 放射性物質會飄到大陸上空\NDisaster. There'll be fallout all over the mainland.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.16,1:34:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是美國海軍弗林艦 準備攻擊\NUSS Flynn... Prepare to engage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.10,1:34:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小艇轉彎了\NThe boat is turning, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.44,1:34:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰在開船\NWho's driving that boat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.44,1:34:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是拉普\NRapp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.78,1:35:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去接他\NGo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.91,1:35:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 長官您說什麼 - 去接他\N- Sir? - Go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.25,1:35:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢\NWhat are you doing? Hurley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.06,1:35:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利\NHurley?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.19,1:35:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把他救上來\NTrying to get our boy to throw the bomb in the water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.73,1:35:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗林艦 準備好了就可以開火\NFlynn, you are clear to fire when ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.33,1:35:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開火 小艇已經掉頭了\NDo not fire, Commander. The boat is turning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.30,1:35:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不攻擊的話 核彈遲早會爆炸\NIf we don't engage, that guarantees detonation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.30,1:35:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這風險很大\NI understand there's a risk,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.47,1:35:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我們最好的機會了\Nbut this is the best chance we've got.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.04,1:35:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽的\NShit! God damn it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.04,1:35:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那呢\NThere he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.95,1:35:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調至海軍無線電頻段\NGet me on that boat's marine bandwidth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.89,1:35:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普\NRapp!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.49,1:35:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普\NRapp!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.19,1:35:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到我了麼 用無線電接聽\NCan you hear me? Pick up the radio!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.82,1:35:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把炸彈從船上扔下去\NThrow the bomb overboard!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.76,1:35:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我要帶它離艦隊遠點\NNo way, sir, I gotta get further away from the fleet!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.96,1:35:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普\NRapp!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.36,1:36:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽的這輩子 就服從我的命令行不行\NFor once in your life, take a goddamn order!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.17,1:36:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第六艦隊要朝你開火了\NThe Sixth Fleet is about to blow you to hell!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.18,1:36:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮部 這裏是德爾塔二隊 炸彈落入水中\NCommand, Delta Two, the bomb's in the water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.88,1:36:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官 別開火 - 核彈落入水中\NCommander, hold your fire! The bomb's in the water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.08,1:36:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 弗林艦 別開火\NFlynn, hold fire!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.05,1:36:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開火\NHold fire!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.12,1:36:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開火\NHold fire!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.55,1:36:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有30秒撤離\NGot less than 30 seconds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.39,1:37:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 我們撤\NAll right, go! Get outta here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.11,1:37:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NJesus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.47,1:38:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意 準備撞擊\NBrace for impact.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.34,1:38:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官\NSir, yes, sir!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.08,1:38:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NHoly shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.12,1:38:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓穩了\NHold on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.20,1:39:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.70,1:39:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不該來救我的\NYou shouldn't have come for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.41,1:39:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要習慣我們經常這麼干 小子\NDon't get used to it, son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.58,1:40:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利\NHurley...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.25,1:40:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎我們能安全撤出去了\NLooks like we're gonna be all right up here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.38,1:40:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼覺得的\NI think.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.06,1:40:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請匯報受損程度\NDamage control central. Report.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.02,1:40:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓力值正常\NPressure is normalizing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.39,1:40:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船體多處受損\NWe have multiple hull breaches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.59,1:40:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾森豪威爾號 輻射值如何\NRadiologicals, Eisenhower?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.43,1:40:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輻射值低\NLow... Low levels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.53,1:40:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動清潔措施\NInitiating countermeasure wash-down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.00,1:40:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 指揮官 傷亡人數多少\NCommander, any casualties?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.74,1:40:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 弗林號受損嚴重\NThe Flynn took some serious damage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.70,1:40:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尚未收到傷亡人數報告 要是炸彈沒有在水下爆炸\NThe casualty reports aren't in yet,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.67,1:40:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估計我們都完蛋了\Nbut if it had gone off above the waterline, I don't think we'd be here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.71,1:40:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾森豪威爾號\NEisenhower,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.31,1:40:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願上帝保佑你們\Nmy prayers are with you all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.30,1:41:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾利 拉普在麼\NHurley, is Rapp there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.20,1:41:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下\NHold on a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.47,1:41:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 說吧\NYeah, go ahead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.71,1:41:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 你沒事吧\NYou okay, Mitch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.38,1:41:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我挺棒的\NOh, yeah. I'm fantastic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.22,1:41:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天拯救了很多人的性命\NYou saved a lot of lives today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.05,1:41:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有不少人犧牲了\NTook some losses, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.65,1:42:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪拜 阿聯酋\NWhat the hell are you looking at?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.45,1:42:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛這麼盯著我看\NYou look like a mummy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.28,1:42:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來像個木乃伊一樣\NYeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.65,1:42:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\NWell...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.72,1:42:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木乃伊可不用寫這些報告\NA mummy doesn't have to write up reports.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.85,1:42:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你口述吧 你挺擅長做報告的\NDictate them. You should be good at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.46,1:42:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯塔米將軍\NIranian official, General Rostami,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.19,1:42:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊朗少數反對派領導人 在德黑蘭\Nthe leader of the minority opposition in Tehran,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.20,1:42:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲稱他有證據表明 美國中情局內部\Nclaims that he has proof that a secret group{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.56,1:42:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個秘密暗殺組織\Nof assassins within America's CIA{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.83,1:42:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該對上周的核爆炸事件負責\Nare responsible for last week's nuclear event.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.60,1:42:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊朗總統選舉\NWith the Iranian presidential election{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.47,1:42:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩周後即將舉行\Njust two weeks away,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.21,1:43:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯塔米將軍受歡迎程度正在上升\NGeneral Rostami continues to rise in popularity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.57,1:43:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說羅斯塔米將軍\NThey say General Rostami is{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.21,1:43:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是下一屆伊朗總統\Ngonna be the next President of Iran.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.88,1:43:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\NYeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.71,1:43:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在不必把以色列炸平 就能當上總統了\NHe didn't even have to blow up Israel to get there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.58,1:43:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說 他還真是個大麻煩\NHe's gonna be a major pain in the ass, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.58,1:43:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉普在哪 我聯繫不上他\NWhere's Rapp? I can't reach him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.19,1:43:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會知道\NHow the hell do I know where Rapp is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.85,1:43:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是個醫院裏的木乃伊罷了\NI'm a mummy in a hospital.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.42,1:43:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯塔米全力支持\NRostami has full support for restarting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.72,1:43:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重啟伊朗核項目\NIran's nuclear program.{\r}

